data.description: A gorgeous desert view home on a half acre lot in a quiet cul-de-sac neighborhood is ready for you! This spacious 4 bedroom, 3 bath home has everything and more. Newly landscaped front and back yards feature low maintenance turf, lava rock and mulch, mature trees, oleanders, bamboo and more. RV access with automatic gate and pavers with easy in and out access are a must-have for your desert toys! A large covered front porch is the perfect place to watch the sunrise with your morning coffee. Enter through the custom front door to see the open concept formal living and dining rooms and beautiful raised ceilings. Central to the home is the very large kitchen with newer stainless steel appliances and large walk-in pantry. You'll have plenty of space to make your next gourmet meal and entertain guests. The family room features a stone fireplace with a wood burning stove to really help warm you up on those cold desert nights. Adjacent to the kitchen, you will find a large laundry room with wash sink and plenty of storage for all of your household cleaning supplies. The finished three car garage includes custom built-in cabinetry for all of your organizational needs. As you head down the hallway, you will find a convenient hall bathroom for guests as well as ample floor to ceiling linen closest. The primary bedroom suite faces the back of the home and has its own access to the back yard. This room features raised ceilings, large windows, and a huge walk-in closet. The primary bathroom includes two sinks, a soaking tub and a separate stand-up shower. The other three bedrooms are all large with big windows and feature large closets with built-in shelving. Let's not forget about this home's amazing back yard and the view! You'll be able to enjoy a nice meal under your covered patio, stargaze and enjoy the city lights in the far distance. The mature trees, oleanders, and the same new turf and volcano rock featured in the front landscaping tie everything in.
